snippet.title: Johnny Depp says he is being boycotted by Hollywood because of Amber Heard's Drama
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp says he is being boycotted because of Amber Heard's Drama. Famous film and television actress Amber Heard is being called out for lying on numerous occasions by various celebrities. One such celebrity is her ex-husband and Golden Globe winner Johnny Depp.
So, will Johnny be able to prove that Amber has been lying all this while or is it ultimately both of them who are responsible for this chaos equally? Only time will tell.
That’s all for today. I hope you liked the video. If you did make sure to hit that like button and subscribe to the channel so that you never miss any amazing video from us.
